CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, pg. A16 reads: "Anyone For Dimples? - Gloria Sweeney shows her dimples as she models a hat and dress for the D.I. show."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Gloria Sweeney wearing light colored dress with short sleeves, belt, and light colored gloves, holding hat with ribbon, standing in home of Gloria Grate, in preparation for the D.I.'s "Atlantic City U.S.A" revue held in the Press Club of the Hotel Sherwyn
